要的个人数据。</p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:start;"> <span style=""><b>[7.1] 美国司法部针对谷歌的反垄断案开始审理，行业影响重大。 —</b></span> <a class="link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/09/06/technology/modern-internet-first-monopoly-trial-us-google-dominance.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">The New York Times</a></p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;">美国司法部针对谷歌的反垄断案件即将开始审理，该案件指控该公司在在线搜索领域非法滥用权力，扼杀竞争。谷歌组建了一支强大的辩护团队，并在法律费用和游说方面投入了大量资源。该审判的结果可能对科技行业产生深远影响，有可能导致主要互联网公司的监管或分拆。</p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:start;"> <b>Want to read more?</b></p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:start;"> See additional news on <a class="link" href="https://www.newsminimalist.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">newsminimalist.com</a> .</p><hr class="content_break"><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:start;"> Thanks for reading us and see you tomorrow,</p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:start;"> Vadim </p></div><div class='beehiiv__footer'><br class='beehiiv__footer__break'><hr class='beehiiv__footer__line'> <a target="_blank" class="beehiiv__footer_link" style="text-align: center;" href="https://www.beehiiv.com/?utm_campaign=dc604bf3-cf5d-4f47-9619-dd2f8bdf316e&amp;utm_medium=post_rss&amp;utm_source=news_minimalist_daily">Powered by beehiiv</a></div></div> ;
